# Changelog
v1.2.0 - 07.09.2022
* Using latest Ubuntu ISO 20.04.5
* Set VM version to 17 (vSphere 7)
* Updated build process to HCL2 and HTTP file provisioning

v1.1.3 - 08.09.2021 
* Update VM version to 19 (ESX 7.0.2)
* Updating base ISO to point-release 3

v1.1.2 - 20.05.2021
- Fixing an issue when `apt update` failed because of required interactive input

v1.1.1 - 18.04.2021
- Clearing machine-id for proper DHCP leases

v1.1.0 - 22.02.2021
* Updated to LTS 20.04.2 ISO
* Increased SSH timeout for automatic updates
* Configured a root password

v1.0.0 - 27.08.2020
* Initial version building a Ubuntu LTS 20.04 OVA

# Legend

* : Internal changes
+ : New features
